displayProperties.name: Iceflare Bolts
displayProperties.description: An unseeing yet all-knowing stare fixed eternally to a solitary point. You track your enemies with blade-like precision.

displayProperties.name: Frostpulse
displayProperties.description: A conflux trapped motionless in crystal; infinite possibilities held in tranquil inertia. You unleash the Darkness within, suspending your enemies in harrowing stillness.

displayProperties.name: Tectonic Harvest
displayProperties.description: A petrified grip, grasping for something once held but now lost. Your hands create power from nothing.

displayProperties.name: Cryoclasm
displayProperties.description: An ageless consciousness, crystallized, contained within a single moment. The imprisoned shatter at your approach.

displayProperties.name: Adaptive Frame
displayProperties.description: A well-rounded grip, reliable and sturdy.

displayProperties.name: Rose
displayProperties.description: In his strong hand the man held a Rose. And his aura burned bright.

displayProperties.name: Shatterdive
displayProperties.description: A frozen scream trapped in gemstone; the recognition of a great and terrible truth. You descend upon your enemies with the enormity of the Dark.

displayProperties.name: Winter's Shroud
displayProperties.description: A desire for legacy, to be known, preserved in sterile glass. The world stops and starts at your command.
